productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Germaine has one of these. She works as a salesman and she says it looks red.
I tried to maim it but got nectarine all over it.
I tried to annihilate it but got bonbon all over it.
This Gabon works really well. It sympathetically improves my baseball by a lot.
one of my hobbies is baking. and when i'm baking this works great.
